<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَولِيَاءَ}</span> ... آلِهَةً يَتَوَلَّوْنَهَا، وَيَعْبُدُونَهَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَفِيظٌ}</span> ... رَقِيبٌ عَتِيدٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُمَّ الْقُرَى}</span> ... مَكَّةَ؛ وَالمُرَادُ أَهْلُهَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا رَيْبَ فِيهِ}</span> ... لَا شَكَّ فيِ مَجِيئِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
