<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَإِلَيْهِ أُنِيبُ}</span> ... إِلَيْهِ أَرْجِعُ فِي كُلِّ الأُمُورِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَاطِرُ}</span> ... خَالِقُ، وَمُبْدِعُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمِنَ الْأَنْعَامِ أَزْوَاجًا}</span> ... أَنْوَاعًا؛ ذُكُورًا، وَإِنَاثًا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَذْرَؤُكُمْ فِيهِ}</span> ... يُكَثِّرُكُمْ؛ بِسَبَبِ التَّزْوِيجِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَقَالِيدُ السَّمَوَاتِ}</span> ... مِلْكُهَا، وَمَفَاتِيحُ خَزَائِنِهَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
